rows.label: qst103609_msg0002
rows.name:
It was a Superbian! He had
a very tense atmosphere.

rows.label: qst103609_msg0003
rows.name:
He was heading towards
the Great Stairway.

rows.label: qst103609_msg0004
rows.name:
Not many people go there, so be
careful if you're heading that way.

rows.label: qst103609_msg0101
rows.name: What would a Superbian want there?

rows.label: qst103609_msg0102
rows.name:
I hope it doesn't cause any
unnecessary trouble...

rows.label: qst103609_msg0201
rows.name:
I got curious, so I went to
the Great Stairway to see.

rows.label: qst103609_msg0202
rows.name:
The Superbian I saw earlier
was collapsed there, so I
took him to a doctor.

rows.label: qst103609_msg0203
rows.name:
No need for thanks! Even if he's
from the Empire, I can't just
leave someone who's collapsed.
